---
/**
 * ConverterPlaceholder - 파일 변환 섹션 (플레이스홀더)
 * Issue #16에서 React Island로 교체 예정
 */
---

<section id="convert" class="my-16 p-10 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-white max-w-[720px] mx-auto max-sm:p-6 max-sm:my-12">
  <h2 class="font-serif text-[22px] font-normal text-center mb-1">파일 변환</h2>
  <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-7">
    PDF를 업로드하면 Notion 호환 마크다운으로 변환합니다
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
    <!-- 파일 선택 버튼 -->
    <button
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-2.5
             bg-black text-white border-none rounded-sm
             text-[15px] font-medium cursor-pointer hover:opacity-85 transition-opacity"
    >
      <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4" />
        <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8" />
        <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15" />
      </svg>
      파일 선택
    </button>
    <span class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 -mt-1">PDF · 최대 50MB</span>

    <!-- 드롭존 -->
    <div
      class="w-full border-[1.5px] border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-md
             py-7 px-6 text-center bg-white min-h-[80px]
             flex items-center justify-center"
    >
      <span class="text-[13px] text-gray-500">또는 여기에 PDF를 드래그 앤 드롭</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 변환 버튼 -->
  <button
    disabled
    class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full mt-4 py-3 px-6
           bg-gray-300 text-gray-500 border-none rounded-sm
           text-[15px] font-medium cursor-not-allowed"
  >
    마크다운으로 변환
  </button>
</section>
